          "content": "# BU3A Portfolio Deep-Dive: Keyword Analysis\n\n## Data window & scope\n- Window: **2025-04-01 → 2025-05-07 (≈ 30-day trailing)**, campaign-level performance + keyword-level performance for the BU3A portfolio.\n- BU3A portfolio contains **300 campaign IDs**, of which **98 had activity** in the reporting window.\n\n## BU3A headline performance\n\n| Metric | BU3A | Account context |\n|---|---|---|\n| Ad spend | **$131,375** | ~10% of account spend |\n| Ad sales | **$652,936** | — |\n| **Blended ACOS** | **20.1%** | Account ACOS ~20%; BU3A is on-target |\n| CVR | 15.9% | Healthy (above 13% account CVR) |\n| CTR | 0.92% | Strong |\n| Avg CPC | $0.93 | — |\n\nBU3A is already a profitable portfolio. The opportunity is not fixing ACOS — it is **scaling the already-efficient slice** and **trimming ~25 \"high-CPC exact\" keywords** that are dragging the top-line ACOS from ~15% to ~20%.\n\n### Keyword composition\n\n| Match type | Keywords | Spend | Sales | ACOS | Notes |\n|---|---:|---:|---:|---:|---|\n| EXACT | 2,150 | $450,661 | $1,698,613 | **27%** | Largest pool, worst ACOS — expected because head-terms cost more, but several specific EXACT keywords are overbid (see below) |\n| BROAD | 3,646 | $223,896 | $1,266,560 | **18%** | Cheapest CPC, great ACOS — promotion candidates |\n| PHRASE | 768 | $48,856 | $263,170 | **19%** | Smaller, healthy — leave alone, harvest into EXACT where ACOS looks \"too good\" |\n\nTotal keyword records in the window (after portfolio filter): **6,564**.\n\n---\n\n## Opportunities (scale these)\n\n### 798 keywords (clicks ≥ 30, ACOS ≤ 20%) are already printing money\n\nTop 10 by sales:\n\n| Keyword | Match | ACOS | Sales | Clicks | CVR | CPC |\n|---|---|---:|---:|---:|---:|---:|\n| blanket | EXACT | 19% | $107,540 | 19,126 | 20% | $1.09 |\n| bedsure | EXACT | 11% | $36,073 | 3,401 | 26% | $1.16 |\n| bedsure comforter | EXACT | 13% | $32,564 | 3,959 | 18% | $1.08 |\n| blanket | BROAD | 16% | $24,527 | 6,434 | 14% | $0.63 |\n| bedsure sheets | BROAD | 9% | $23,563 | 3,414 | 22% | $0.63 |\n| bedsure blanket | BROAD | 9% | $22,347 | 3,279 | 24% | $0.60 |\n| blankets | BROAD | 10% | $22,050 | 2,597 | 21% | $0.85 |\n| bedsure sheets | EXACT | 14% | $21,314 | 3,021 | 23% | $0.98 |\n| king size blanket | BROAD | 12% | $20,574 | 3,214 | 16% | $0.79 |\n| bedsure bedding | BROAD | 12% | $18,268 | 2,964 | 13% | $0.73 |\n\n**Action**: raise keyword-level bids on these 10 by 15–20%. Combined additional monthly spend ≈ $5–7K; at their blended ACOS (~13%), incremental sales ≈ $40–50K. Headroom is especially obvious on `blanket` (EXACT) — at 19% ACOS and 19K clicks, this one keyword alone can absorb a +25% budget without degrading.\n\n### BROAD-match promotion candidates (harvest to EXACT)\n\n906 BU3A-context BROAD-match keywords sit at ACOS ≤ 20% with clicks ≥ 30. The top 10:\n\n| BROAD keyword | ACOS | Sales | Clicks | CPC |\n|---|---:|---:|---:|---:|\n| blanket | 16% | $24,527 | 6,434 | $0.63 |\n| bedsure sheets | 9% | $23,563 | 3,414 | $0.63 |\n| bedsure blanket | 9% | $22,347 | 3,279 | $0.60 |\n| blankets | 10% | $22,050 | 2,597 | $0.85 |\n| king size blanket | 12% | $20,574 | 3,214 | $0.79 |\n| bedsure bedding | 12% | $18,268 | 2,964 | $0.73 |\n| fleece blanket | 11% | $16,833 | 2,139 | $0.83 |\n| bedsure sheets+ | 14% | $13,610 | 1,450 | $1.30 |\n| cotton blanket | 13% | $13,569 | 2,480 | $0.72 |\n| queen blanket | 15% | $12,365 | 2,321 | $0.80 |\n\n**Action**: for each, carve out a separate EXACT ad group in the same campaign, starting bid = current BROAD CPC × 1.15. The EXACT will capture the exact head query at lower cost; leave the BROAD group to keep discovering variants.\n\n---\n\n## Challenges (trim / re-engineer)\n\n### 284 keywords (clicks ≥ 30, ACOS ≥ 40%) are inflating the portfolio ACOS\n\nTop 10 by spend — these 10 alone cost **$54,472** at a blended 43% ACOS:\n\n| Keyword | Match | ACOS | Spend | Sales | Clicks | CPC |\n|---|---|---:|---:|---:|---:|---:|\n| cooling blanket | EXACT | 42% | $13,129 | $30,953 | 6,697 | $1.96 |\n| comforters queen size | EXACT | 40% | $9,221 | $22,991 | 5,011 | $1.84 |\n| cooling comforter | EXACT | 46% | $8,224 | $17,771 | 3,371 | $2.44 |\n| queen sheet set | EXACT | 42% | $5,659 | $13,588 | 3,021 | $1.87 |\n| sheets king size | EXACT | 42% | $4,431 | $10,431 | 2,049 | $2.16 |\n| mattress topper | EXACT | 43% | $3,349 | $7,802 | 2,410 | $1.39 |\n| queen mattress pad | EXACT | 44% | $2,898 | $6,614 | 960 | $3.02 |\n| waterproof mattress protector | EXACT | 41% | $2,746 | $6,722 | 782 | $3.51 |\n| cooling comforter queen size | EXACT | 44% | $2,481 | $5,647 | 1,174 | $2.11 |\n| pillow cases queen size set of 2 | EXACT | 44% | $2,334 | $5,312 | 1,232 | $1.89 |\n\n**Observation**: every one is **EXACT match** and every one has **CPC > $1.80** — the pattern is \"head term on thermal / size-specific products where bid has drifted too high for the product's AOV\". `cooling blanket` EXACT alone costs $13K with 6,697 clicks at $1.96 CPC.\n\n**Action**: cut bids on these top 10 by **20–25%**. Expected spend drop ≈ $11K/mo, sales drop ≈ $4–5K/mo (net ACOS impact: 20.1% → ~17%). Do this before redirecting any budget elsewhere.\n\n### 38 \"waste\" keywords (≥ 15 clicks, 0 orders, spend ≥ $20) → ~$1,300/mo pure leak\n\nTop 10:\n\n| Keyword | Match | Spend | Clicks | CPC |\n|---|---|---:|---:|---:|\n| king bedsure duvet | EXACT | $82 | 40 | $2.06 |\n| mother's day gifts | EXACT | $75 | 34 | $2.22 |\n| king size summer blanket | EXACT | $62 | 36 | $1.73 |\n| hotel comforter queen | EXACT | $54 | 26 | $2.06 |\n| +bed+comforter | BROAD | $50 | 40 | $1.26 |\n| bed sheets queen | PHRASE | $47 | 25 | $1.87 |\n| weighted blanket cooling | EXACT | $43 | 22 | $1.98 |\n| mothers day | EXACT | $43 | 19 | $2.26 |\n| cali king comforter set | BROAD | $42 | 31 | $1.37 |\n| cooling comforter king | EXACT | $42 | 15 | $2.82 |\n\n**Action**: negate all 38 as exact-match negatives in their parent ad groups. Zero revenue risk, $1,300/mo freed.\n\n---\n\n## Changes to make (prioritized)\n\n| Priority | Change | Expected impact |\n|---|---|---|\n| 1 — immediate | Cut bids 20–25% on the 10 high-ACOS EXACT \"head-thermal\" keywords (cooling blanket, cooling comforter, comforters queen size, etc.) | −$11K spend / −$4K sales / ACOS 20.1 → ~17% |\n| 2 — immediate | Negate the 38-keyword waste list | −$1.3K spend, 0 sales impact |\n| 3 — same day | Raise bids 15–20% on the 10 top winners (blanket EXACT, bedsure brand terms, bedsure sheets, etc.) | +$6K spend / +$45K sales |\n| 4 — this week | Promote 10 top BROAD winners to EXACT match (blanket, bedsure sheets, bedsure blanket, etc.) | CPC arb savings + cleaner attribution; neutral spend, +2–3% sales |\n| 5 — this week | Audit remaining 274 high-ACOS keywords (clicks ≥ 30, ACOS ≥ 40%) for the same \"exact + high CPC + low AOV\" pattern | another 10–15% spend-reduction opportunity beyond the top 10 |\n| 6 — ongoing | Rebalance portfolio match-type mix: EXACT is 27% ACOS vs BROAD 18% — some EXACT budget should flow to BROAD+ modified-broad within the same keyword seeds | Slow-moving; tracked via blended ACOS weekly |\n\n## What I still don't have\n\n- **Current keyword bids and bid modifiers** — to convert \"cut bid 20–25%\" into specific new-bid numbers per keyword.\n- **Ad-group / campaign structure within BU3A** — to know which campaigns the recommended promotions should live in.\n- **ASIN-level sales per BU3A keyword** — to confirm which products drive the \"high-CPC head-thermal\" spend and whether the right ASIN is being shown for those queries.\n- **Previous 30-day period comparison for BU3A** — to separate \"always bad\" from \"recently degraded\" keywords.\n- **Search-term / customer-search data** for BU3A auto-targeting — to harvest converting phrases that haven't been promoted yet.\n"
