          "label": "GPT 5.5",
          "content": "# Yesterday Budget Pacing Review\n\nQuestion: Quickly analyze which campaigns did not spend their full budget yesterday and the main reasons; then analyze which campaigns hit their budget very early in the day and the reasons for that.\n\nBusiness data used: yesterday campaign performance, daily campaign budget settings, and campaign delivery status/reason snapshots. Time basis follows the business data: 2026-05-07 for performance, with the campaign status snapshot used to identify out-of-budget delivery reasons. Currency values are reported as provided by the business data.\n\n## Executive read\n\nThis answer corrects the earlier parsing issue: the campaign performance data is not empty. Yesterday performance totals are spend $45,412.97, sales $58,861.43, orders 1,552, and clicks 35,549. The data does not contain hourly spend, so “very early” is inferred from out-of-budget delivery reasons, not from an exact hour-of-day cutoff.\n\n## Campaigns that likely did not use full budget\n\n| campaign | budget | spend | budget use | clicks | orders | sales | likely reason |\n| --- | ---: | ---: | ---: | ---: | ---: | ---: | --- |\n| Xnurta AI BU3A-lyh【法兰绒毯-素色-QU-烟灰】SP精准-blanket-企业购Boost | $650.00 | $78.20 | 12.0% | 61 | 5 | $136.94 | low traffic or bid/target reach; campaign was still delivering at snapshot |\n| Xnurta AI BU3A-GH【被子-全涤-素色-QU-白色】SP定位-down comforter相关竞对 | $670.47 | $114.42 | 17.1% | 93 | 4 | $139.48 | low traffic or bid/target reach; campaign was still delivering at snapshot |\n| BU3A-GH【被子-全涤-素色-KI-白色】SP定位-down comforter相关竞对 | $500.00 | $69.15 | 13.8% | 44 | 3 | $225.45 | low traffic or bid/target reach; campaign was still delivering at snapshot |\n| BU3A-GH【被子-全涤-素色-KI-白色】SP定位-直接竞对 | $400.00 | $68.29 | 17.1% | 46 | 4 | $174.86 | low traffic or bid/target reach; campaign was still delivering at snapshot |\n| Xnurta AI BU3A-GH【被子-全涤-素色-QU+KI-白色】SP类目-Bedding Comforters | $364.30 | $44.93 | 12.3% | 61 | 2 | $66.74 | low traffic or bid/target reach; campaign was still delivering at snapshot |\n| BU3A-GH【被子-全涤-素色-KI-白色】SP广泛-多词根混投 | $300.00 | $33.63 | 11.2% | 33 | 1 | $45.09 | low traffic or bid/target reach; campaign was still delivering at snapshot |\n\n## Campaigns that hit budget / stopped delivery\n\n| campaign | budget | spend | budget use | clicks | orders | sales | delivery reason | action |\n| --- | ---: | ---: | ---: | ---: | ---: | ---: | --- | --- |\n| BU3A-GH【被子-全涤-素色-KI-白色】SP精准-KI+Duvet/Duvet Insert-搜索页 | $800.00 | $707.30 | 88.4% | 197 | 13 | $676.46 | CAMPAIGN_OUT_OF_BUDGET | do not simply add budget; fix efficiency first |\n| BU4A-小熊【床单组-竹纤维-素色-KI-鲍鱼壳灰】SP精准-规格词 | $210.00 | $221.78 | 105.6% | 37 | 9 | $611.39 | CAMPAIGN_OUT_OF_BUDGET | do not simply add budget; fix efficiency first |\n| BU4-德明【枕套组-竹纤维-素色-KI-多色】SP自动 | $100.00 | $79.79 | 79.8% | 117 | 15 | $532.43 | CAMPAIGN_OUT_OF_BUDGET | increase budget only if margin supports it |\n| BU3A-GH【被子-全涤-素色-QU-白色】SP定位-多件套 | $1.00 | $706.83 | 70683.0% | 489 | 13 | $530.27 | CAMPAIGN_OUT_OF_BUDGET | do not simply add budget; fix efficiency first |\n| BU3A-Enos【床垫罩-全涤壳-磨毛布压花-KI-白色】SP精准-king size mattress protect… | $150.00 | $102.61 | 68.4% | 39 | 13 | $441.36 | CAMPAIGN_OUT_OF_BUDGET | increase budget only if margin supports it |\n| BU3A-YH【毛毯-全棉-小肌理棉毯-人字纹-TW XL-多色】SP广泛-规格材质词 | $50.00 | $49.56 | 99.1% | 51 | 6 | $404.92 | CAMPAIGN_OUT_OF_BUDGET | increase budget only if margin supports it |\n\n## Data still needed\n\nTo say exactly which campaigns ran out “very early,” hourly spend or budget-depletion timestamp data is still needed.\n"
