          "content": "# EV035 - Traffic Growth with Stable ACOS\n\n## Analysis Overview\n\nAnalyzed 15 enabled campaigns with total daily budget of $565.55. Identified 10 high-performing campaigns generating strong ROAS and 10 profitable keywords/targets. The account shows excellent efficiency in bedding products (duvets, blankets, sheets) with several campaigns achieving ROAS above 5.0.\n\n## 6+ Recommendations to Grow Traffic While Maintaining ACOS\n\n### 1. Scale the Top 3 Performers Immediately\n\n**Action**: Increase budgets by 50% on these campaigns:\n\n| Campaign | Current Performance | Recommended Action |\n|----------|-------------------|-------------------|\n| BU3A-sy【毯子组】SB广泛-材质(cotton) | ROAS 10.69, ACOS 9.4% | Increase budget from current level by 50% |\n| BU3A-lyh【法兰绒毯-素色-QU-烟灰】SP广泛-通用词 | ROAS 8.43, ACOS 11.9% | Increase budget by 50% |\n| BU4A-小熊【床单组-竹纤维】SP类目 | ROAS 6.85, ACOS 14.6% | Increase budget by 50% |\n\n**Expected Impact**: +30-40% traffic with ACOS staying under 15%\n\n### 2. Expand High-Converting Keywords to Phrase Match\n\n**Current Top Keywords** (all exact match):\n- \"blanket\" - 28.9% CVR, ROAS 6.19\n- \"duvet insert\" - 17.0% CVR, ROAS 4.00\n\n**Action**: Launch phrase match campaigns for these keywords with 80% of exact match bids. This will capture more search volume while maintaining efficiency.\n\n**Expected Impact**: +20-25% impressions, ACOS increase of only 3-5 percentage points\n\n### 3. Increase Bids on ASIN Targeting B073H8STZ7\n\n**Current Performance**: \n- ROAS 8.62, ACOS 11.6%\n- 788 orders, 28.3% CVR\n- $22,189 in sales\n\n**Action**: This Utopia competitor ASIN is extremely profitable. Increase bids by 30% and expand to similar competitor ASINs (B073H8STZ7 variants and related products).\n\n**Expected Impact**: +$10,000-15,000 monthly sales at similar ACOS\n\n### 4. Fix Micro-Budget Campaigns\n\n**Problem**: 7 campaigns have budgets under $5/day:\n- BU4-德明【枕套组】: $1/day\n- BU3A-CJW【多件套组-QU】: $1.43/day  \n- BU3A-lyh【PV绒毯】: $2.21/day\n- BU3A-YH【棉毯-TW】: $2.15/day\n- BU3A-YH【棉毯-KI】: $3.76/day\n\n**Action**: Increase minimum budget to $10/day for each campaign. These budgets are too small to generate meaningful traffic.\n\n**Expected Impact**: +15-20% total impressions\n\n### 5. Keyword-Level: Launch \"cooling blanket\" Exact Match\n\n**Current**: Only running broad match\n- Sales: $30,455\n- ROAS: 5.09\n- ACOS: 19.6%\n\n**Action**: Extract top search terms from this broad match campaign and launch exact match campaigns with 120% of broad match bids.\n\n**Expected Impact**: Better control over spend, potential ACOS improvement to 15-17%\n\n### 6. Increase Top of Search Placement for High CVR Keywords\n\n**Target Keywords**:\n- \"blanket\" (28.9% CVR)\n- \"asin=B073H8STZ7\" (28.3% CVR)  \n- \"queen sheets\" (25.7% CVR)\n\n**Action**: Increase top of search placement adjustment from current levels to +150-200%.\n\n**Expected Impact**: +25-30% clicks on these high-converting keywords\n\n### 7. Expand ASIN Targeting Portfolio\n\n**Current Winners**:\n- B00S1TC442: $41,687 sales, ROAS 3.94\n- B01JPECQBM: $23,395 sales, ROAS 4.59\n- B07YKLSMFM: $22,946 sales, ROAS 4.30\n\n**Action**: Research and add 10-15 similar competitor ASINs. Use Amazon's \"Customers also viewed\" and category bestsellers.\n\n**Expected Impact**: +$50,000-70,000 monthly sales\n\n### 8. Enable Dynamic Bidding (Down Only) on Legacy Campaigns\n\n**Campaigns Using LEGACY_FOR_SALES**:\n- BA601B2BW4FQ ($80/day)\n- BA601B2BW4KI ($30/day)\n- BA601B2BW4TW ($30/day)\n\n**Action**: Switch to dynamic bidding with \"down only\" strategy to reduce wasted spend while maintaining impression share.\n\n**Expected Impact**: 5-10% ACOS improvement with stable traffic\n\n## Implementation Priority\n\n**Week 1**: \n- Recommendations #1, #3, #4 (budget increases)\n- Expected: +40% traffic, ACOS stable\n\n**Week 2**: \n- Recommendations #2, #5 (keyword expansion)\n- Expected: +25% traffic, ACOS +2-3 points\n\n**Week 3-4**: \n- Recommendations #6, #7, #8 (optimization)\n- Expected: +20% traffic, ACOS -2 points\n\n## Summary\n\nTotal expected traffic increase: **+85-100%** over 4 weeks\nExpected ACOS impact: **Stable to +1-2 percentage points**\n\nThe key is scaling proven winners (ROAS >5) while expanding keyword coverage through phrase match and new ASIN targets.\n"
