          "label": "Sonnet 4.6",
          "content": "# Top 10 Keywords That Most Need Optimization\n\n**Data window:** 2026-04-08 to 2026-05-07 (30 days)  \n**Account:** Firefly Buys (US)  \n**Report rows:** 42,604 daily keyword records → 2,135 unique keyword+matchType combinations → 811 with meaningful activity (≥5 clicks or ≥$5 spend)  \n**Total active keyword spend:** $48,206.63 | Total purchases: 5,517\n\n---\n\n## Optimization Scoring Methodology\n\nKeywords were ranked by a composite waste score based on:\n1. **High spend with zero conversions** – worst ROI, pure waste\n2. **High ACOS (>100%)** – unprofitable; spending more than earning\n3. **Very low CTR (<0.3%) with high impressions** – poor relevance/listing match\n4. **Low CVR with high clicks** – traffic not converting\n\n---\n\n## Top 10 Keywords Needing Optimization\n\n| # | Keyword | Match | Impressions | Clicks | Spend | Purchases | Sales | ACOS | CTR% | CVR% | CPC |\n|---|---------|-------|------------|--------|-------|-----------|-------|------|------|------|-----|\n| 1 | helmet | PHRASE | 309,119 | 767 | $549.58 | 32 | $2,782.75 | 19.7% | 0.25% | 4.17% | $0.72 |\n| 2 | gun safe | PHRASE | 108,983 | 328 | $1,265.84 | 7 | $897.34 | 141.1% | 0.30% | 2.13% | $3.86 |\n| 3 | dog cooling pad | EXACT | 100,526 | 217 | $323.00 | 47 | $3,131.47 | 10.3% | 0.22% | 21.66% | $1.49 |\n| 4 | cat wipes | EXACT | 7,145 | 19 | $94.04 | 1 | $14.99 | 627.4% | 0.27% | 5.26% | $4.95 |\n| 5 | teeth wipes for dog | EXACT | 15,589 | 39 | $156.22 | 4 | $61.85 | 252.6% | 0.25% | 10.26% | $4.01 |\n| 6 | reloading scale | EXACT | 10,310 | 64 | $166.77 | 1 | $61.95 | 269.2% | 0.62% | 1.56% | $2.61 |\n| 7 | headgear | PHRASE | 43,815 | 30 | $9.61 | 3 | $188.49 | 5.1% | 0.07% | 10.00% | $0.32 |\n| 8 | dog wipes for paws | EXACT | 23,179 | 57 | $158.05 | 10 | $152.36 | 103.7% | 0.25% | 17.54% | $2.77 |\n| 9 | dog dental wipes | EXACT | 22,317 | 100 | $321.69 | 22 | $282.49 | 113.9% | 0.45% | 22.00% | $3.22 |\n| 10 | rechargeable flashlight | PHRASE | 25,993 | 15 | $25.61 | 0 | $0.00 | N/A | 0.06% | 0.00% | $1.71 |\n\n**Top 10 combined spend: $3,070.41 (6.4% of total active spend)**\n\n---\n\n## Detailed Analysis & Recommended Actions\n\n### 1. `helmet` — PHRASE · ACOS 19.7%, CTR 0.25%\n- **Issue:** 309K impressions but only 0.25% CTR — the broad term \"helmet\" attracts irrelevant search queries (football helmets, bike helmets, etc.) to what appears to be lacrosse/sports headgear products.\n- **Action:** Add extensive negative keywords (bike helmet, motorcycle helmet, football helmet, hard hat, etc.). Consider converting winning search terms to EXACT match and reducing PHRASE bid.\n\n### 2. `gun safe` — PHRASE · ACOS 141.1%, Spend $1,265.84\n- **Issue:** Largest single wasted spend. Only 7 purchases against $1,265 spend = $180.83 cost per purchase. Extremely unprofitable.\n- **Action:** Immediate bid reduction (target ACOS likely ~30–40%). Mine search term report for converting sub-queries to move to EXACT and add negative keywords for non-converting variants. Consider pausing if bid cuts don't improve ACOS within 2 weeks.\n\n### 3. `dog cooling pad` — EXACT · ACOS 10.3%, CTR 0.22%\n- **Issue:** Good ACOS and CVR (21.7%) but very low CTR (0.22%) on 100K impressions suggests listing images/title may not match buyer intent or bid is winning low-quality placements.\n- **Action:** Review ad placement report. Optimize main image and title for \"cooling pad.\" Consider raising bid to win top-of-search placements which typically yield higher CTR.\n\n### 4. `cat wipes` — EXACT · ACOS 627.4%, Spend $94\n- **Issue:** Catastrophically unprofitable — spending $94 to generate $15 in sales. The product (dog/pet wipes) likely has poor relevance for \"cat wipes\" shoppers.\n- **Action:** Pause this keyword immediately. Add \"cat\" as a negative keyword across related ad groups if the product is dog-specific.\n\n### 5. `teeth wipes for dog` — EXACT · ACOS 252.6%, Spend $156\n- **Issue:** High intent keyword but ACOS of 252.6% means spending $2.52 for every $1 earned. CPC of $4.01 is very high for a likely low-priced SKU.\n- **Action:** Reduce bid significantly (by ~60%). If product price is under $15, max profitable CPC is ~$0.50–1.00. Verify the product listing is optimized for dental/tooth wipes search intent.\n\n### 6. `reloading scale` — EXACT · ACOS 269.2%, Spend $167\n- **Issue:** Only 1 purchase from 64 clicks. CVR of 1.56% is very low — possible product-keyword mismatch (auto charge pro powder measure vs. \"scale\" intent).\n- **Action:** Review if the Hornady Auto Charge Pro should target \"reloading scale\" — shoppers searching \"scale\" may want a standalone scale, not a powder dispenser. Consider pausing or adding to an ad group with a better-matched product.\n\n### 7. `headgear` — PHRASE · CTR 0.07%, ACOS 5.1%\n- **Issue:** Extremely low CTR (0.07%) on 43K impressions — almost invisible to shoppers. Despite good ACOS when clicked, traffic volume is negligible.\n- **Action:** Improve ad creative (image, headline) to boost CTR. Alternatively, bid down and focus budget on higher-CTR terms. The term \"headgear\" may attract dental/orthodontic searches, so add relevant negatives.\n\n### 8. `dog wipes for paws` — EXACT · ACOS 103.7%, Spend $158\n- **Issue:** Marginally above break-even but likely unprofitable after platform fees and COGS. CVR is healthy (17.5%) but CPC ($2.77) is too high for the likely product price.\n- **Action:** Reduce bid by ~20–30% to target ACOS ~60–70%. Monitor sales volume impact before further cuts.\n\n### 9. `dog dental wipes` — EXACT · ACOS 113.9%, Spend $322\n- **Issue:** Above 100% ACOS — unprofitable. Second-largest spend in the problem list after \"gun safe.\"\n- **Action:** Reduce bid. Target ~50% ACOS. With 22% CVR, this keyword has strong conversion intent; profitability is purely a bid/price issue, not relevance. A bid reduction of ~30% should bring ACOS to target range.\n\n### 10. `rechargeable flashlight` — PHRASE · Zero conversions, CTR 0.06%\n- **Issue:** Zero purchases, CTR of only 0.06% — essentially invisible and unclicked. $25.61 entirely wasted.\n- **Action:** Pause immediately. Product (Amerelle LED Emergency Light) has poor relevance to \"rechargeable flashlight\" — buyers want handheld flashlights, not plug-in nightlights.\n\n---\n\n## Summary\n\n| Category | Keywords | Spend | Purchases | Wasted Spend |\n|----------|----------|-------|-----------|--------------|\n| Zero conversions | 1 | $25.61 | 0 | $25.61 (100%) |\n| ACOS >200% (extreme) | 3 | $417.03 | 6 | ~$380 estimated waste |\n| ACOS 100–200% (unprofitable) | 3 | $1,745.58 | 39 | ~$900 estimated waste |\n| Low CTR / relevance issues | 3 | $882.19 | 82 | Opportunity loss |\n\n**Priority order for action:** Keywords #2 (gun safe), #4 (cat wipes), #10 (rechargeable flashlight) should be actioned immediately (pause or dramatic bid cut). Keywords #5, #6, #9 need bid reductions of 30–60%. Keywords #1, #3, #7 need negative keyword cleanup and creative improvements.\n"
