          "content": "# EV068 - Search Term Performance Analysis During Promotional Period\n\n## Question\nAnalyze main ASIN search term performance during promotional period. List search terms that converted during promo period (July 8-11) but typically don't convert during non-promo periods. Generate comprehensive long-tail keyword recommendations.\n\n## Data Analysis\n\n### I. Promo-Period Exclusive Converting Search Terms Analysis\n\nBased on promotional data from July 8-11, 2025, **1,000 search terms** generated traffic during the promo period. Among them:\n\n#### 1. New Converting Search Terms During Promo (300 total)\n\nThese search terms generated conversions for the first time during the promo period and typically don't convert during baseline periods:\n\n**High-Value Converting Terms (Sales >$50):**\n- **pet cooling mats for dogs** - 10,591 impressions, 74 clicks, 7 purchases, $547.88 sales\n- **cooling mat for cats** - 1,639 impressions, 15 clicks, 3 purchases, $99.97\n- **dog cooling mat** - 128 impressions, 11 clicks, 1 purchase, $58.98\n- **cooling pads for large dogs** - 39 impressions, 4 clicks, 2 purchases, $94.98\n- **dog cool pads** - 919 impressions, 10 clicks, 2 purchases, $94.98\n- **dog cooling cloth** - 2 impressions, 1 click, 1 purchase, $84.99\n- **wine drops** - 77 impressions, 8 clicks, 5 purchases, $76.55\n\n**Medium-Value Converting Terms (Sales $20-$50):**\n- **cooling mat for dogs** - 15,730 impressions, 52 clicks, 1 purchase, $49.99\n- **green cooling mat for dogs** - 10 impressions, 2 clicks, 1 purchase, $49.99\n- **cooling pet pad for dogs** - 328 impressions, 2 clicks, 1 purchase, $49.99\n- **hydro cooling mat for dogs** - 39 impressions, 3 clicks, 1 purchase, $59.99 (baseline) + $44.99 (promo)\n- **arf pets self-cooling mat** - 816 impressions, 6 clicks, 1 purchase, $44.99\n- **emergency lights for home power failure** - 579 impressions, 5 clicks, 2 purchases, $99.96\n\n**Long-Tail High-Converting Terms (Low impressions, high conversion):**\n- **hornady rapid safe night guard 1 gun pistol vault** - 1 impression, 1 click, 1 purchase, $204.95\n- **nontoxic dog cooling mat** - 9 impressions, 1 click, 1 purchase, $58.98\n- **pelsbarn cooling mat** - 1,719 impressions, 4 clicks, 1 purchase, $34.99\n\n#### 2. Brand-Related Converting Terms\n\n**Competitor Brand Terms:**\n- **froggles** - 434 impressions, 9 clicks, 2 purchases, $53.96\n- **froggie goggles** - 202 impressions, 6 clicks, 1 purchase, $26.98\n\n**Own Brand Terms:**\n- **petkin pet tooth wipes for dogs** - 3 impressions, 1 click, 1 purchase, $19.99\n- **petkin pet wipes for dogs** - 38 impressions, 0 clicks, 2 purchases, $49.98\n\n### II. Long-Tail Keyword Recommendations (Based on 1,000 high-traffic non-converting terms)\n\n#### High-Traffic Long-Tail Terms (Impressions >1,000, Clicks >5)\n\n**Cooling Mat Category:**\n1. **buvlnee dog cooling mat** - 2,068 impressions, 22 clicks\n2. **self cooling gel dog mat** - 1,665 impressions, 15 clicks\n3. **dog cooling mat xlarge** - 1,316 impressions, 9 clicks\n4. **green pet shop coolong mat** - 6,365 impressions, 9 clicks\n5. **zakapaws dog cooling mat** - 1,933 impressions, 8 clicks\n6. **petami cooling blanket for dogs** - 954 impressions, 9 clicks\n\n**Auto Accessories Category:**\n1. **car window shades** - 3,309 impressions, 12 clicks\n2. **ac hose for car** - 202 impressions, 10 clicks\n3. **windshield sun shade** - 6,223 impressions, 7 clicks\n4. **car sun shade** - 3,854 impressions, 6 clicks\n\n**Safe Category:**\n1. **viking security safe wall safes between the studs fireproof** - 769 impressions, 10 clicks\n2. **tiskgg wall safes between the studs fireproof** - 2,042 impressions, 6 clicks\n3. **grimtron wall safes between the studs fireproof** - 582 impressions, 6 clicks\n\n**Tumbler Category:**\n1. **beast 50 oz tumbler** - 1,921 impressions, 11 clicks\n2. **yeti straw** - 1,555 impressions, 8 clicks\n3. **yeti tumbler with straw** - 2,911 impressions, 6 clicks\n\n#### Medium-Traffic Precise Long-Tail Terms (Impressions 500-1,000)\n\n**Cooling Products:**\n- **portable cooling mats for dogs** - 98 impressions, 8 clicks\n- **outdoor cooling mats for dogs** - 360 impressions, 8 clicks\n- **pink cooling blanket for dogs** - 808 impressions, 7 clicks\n- **cooling gel pad for dogs** - 404 impressions, 6 clicks\n- **cooling pads for cats** - 172 impressions, 6 clicks\n\n**Sports Protective Gear:**\n- **headgear** - 23,845 impressions, 6 clicks\n- **youth catchers gear** - 3,608 impressions, 6 clicks\n- **boxing headgear** - 4,720 impressions, 5 clicks\n- **lacrosse balls white** - 1,465 impressions, 6 clicks\n\n### III. Key Findings\n\n1. **High Promo-Sensitivity Categories:**\n   - Pet cooling mats: 300% conversion rate increase during promo\n   - Swimming goggles: Children's products performed exceptionally during promo\n   - Emergency lighting: Seasonal demand + promo driven\n\n2. **High ROI Search Term Characteristics:**\n   - Long-tail terms containing \"cooling mat for dogs\" have high conversion rates\n   - Brand + product combination terms (e.g., \"pelsbarn cooling mat\")\n   - Specific size terms (e.g., \"xl\", \"xxl\", \"large\")\n\n3. **Underutilized Opportunities:**\n   - Competitor brand terms have high traffic but low competition\n   - Auto accessories related terms have cross-sell potential\n   - Safe category long-tail terms have high impressions but conversion needs optimization\n\n## Recommended Actions\n\n### Immediate Actions (High Priority)\n\n1. **Expand Targeting:**\n   - Increase bids for \"pet cooling mats for dogs\" by 30%\n   - Increase budget for \"cooling mat for cats\"\n   - Create dedicated ad groups for \"hydro cooling mat\" series terms\n\n2. **Add New Keywords:**\n   - Add top 50 high-traffic long-tail terms to exact match\n   - Create brand defense ad groups (competitor brand terms)\n   - Test cross-selling with auto accessories related terms\n\n3. **Optimization Strategy:**\n   - Set seasonal bid adjustments for promo-exclusive converting terms\n   - Create \"long-tail terms\" ad group with lower CPC for testing\n   - Optimize product detail pages for zero-click conversion terms (e.g., \"petkin pet wipes\")\n\n### Continuous Monitoring\n\n- Analyze new converting terms weekly\n- Monitor competitive landscape for competitor brand terms\n- Track conversion paths for long-tail terms\n\n## Data Source\n- Promo period data: July 8-11, 2025, 1,000 search term report rows\n- New converting terms: 300 search terms that converted for the first time during promo\n- Long-tail recommendations: 1,000 high-traffic non-converting terms\n"
