          "label": "Sonnet 4.5",
          "content": "# EV190: Top-of-Search Placement Modifier Opportunities\n\n## Question\n5 placement-modifier opportunities — campaigns where adding or adjusting a top-of-search modifier would meaningfully shift performance. Justify each with the placement breakdown.\n\n**Period**: April 8 - May 7, 2026 (30 days)\n\n---\n\n## Placement Modifier Opportunities\n\n| Campaign | TOS ACOS | Rest ACOS | TOS CVR | Rest CVR | TOS Share | Recommended Modifier |\n|----------|----------|-----------|---------|----------|-----------|---------------------|\n| Hornady-Fireproof_Keypad_Safe-Branded-PHRASE | 1.8% | N/A (0 sales) | 16.7% | 0% | 20% | +150% |\n| Hornady-Auto_Charge_Pro-Branded-PHRASE | 2.1% | 189% | 11.7% | 1.3% | 4% | +200% |\n| Guardian Sports-GX_Loop-NB-CAT-ASIN-CNQ | 2.4% | 11.4% | 50.0% | 11.1% | 5% | +200% |\n| Hornady-Fireproof_Keypad_Safe-NB-Auto | 2.9% | 24.5% | 18.6% | 2.6% | 5% | +150% |\n| GuardianSports-GX_Loop-Branded-EXACT | 3.1% | 20.3% | 22.3% | 6.7% | 19% | +100% |\n\n**Combined Opportunity**: Shift $1,000+/month to top-of-search placements for 8-10x better ROAS\n\n---\n\n## Detailed Analysis\n\n### 1. Hornady-Fireproof_Keypad_Safe-Branded-PHRASE\n**Current TOS Share**: 20% of impressions (128 of 626)\n\n| Metric | Top of Search | Rest of Search | Difference |\n|--------|---------------|----------------|------------|\n| Spend | $3.74 | $0.77 | - |\n| Sales | $207.95 | $0 | - |\n| Orders | 1 | 0 | - |\n| CVR | 16.7% | 0% | +16.7pp |\n| ACOS | 1.8% | N/A | - |\n| ROAS | 55.6x | 0x | +55.6x |\n\n**Why Increase Modifier:**\n- TOS generates ALL sales despite only 20% of impressions\n- Exceptional 1.8% ACOS vs 0 sales from rest\n- 16.7% CVR shows strong brand intent at top placement\n- Rest of search completely unproductive\n\n**Recommended Modifier**: +150% (2.5x base bid for TOS)\n- Increase TOS impression share from 20% to 50%\n- Expected additional spend: $10/month\n- Expected additional sales: $500/month\n- Projected ACOS: ~2%\n\n---\n\n### 2. Hornady-Auto_Charge_Pro_Powder_Measure-Branded-PHRASE\n**Current TOS Share**: 4% of impressions (1,370 of 34,489)\n\n| Metric | Top of Search | Rest of Search | Difference |\n|--------|---------------|----------------|------------|\n| Spend | $47.55 | $98.14 | - |\n| Sales | $2,312.65 | $51.95 | +4,352% |\n| Orders | 7 | 1 | +600% |\n| CVR | 11.7% | 1.3% | +10.4pp |\n| ACOS | 2.1% | 189% | -187pp |\n| ROAS | 48.6x | 0.5x | +48.1x |\n\n**Why Increase Modifier:**\n- TOS delivers 98% of sales with only 33% of spend\n- Rest of search losing money at 189% ACOS\n- Massive CVR gap (11.7% vs 1.3%)\n- Only 4% of impressions at TOS - huge opportunity\n\n**Recommended Modifier**: +200% (3x base bid for TOS)\n- Increase TOS impression share from 4% to 15%\n- Expected additional spend: $150/month\n- Expected additional sales: $7,000/month\n- Projected ACOS: ~2.5%\n\n**Critical**: Consider negating product pages entirely - 189% ACOS is unsustainable\n\n---\n\n### 3. Guardian Sports-GX_Loop_Headgear-NB-CAT-ASIN-CNQ\n**Current TOS Share**: 5% of impressions (53 of 967)\n\n| Metric | Top of Search | Rest of Search | Difference |\n|--------|---------------|----------------|------------|\n| Spend | $7.66 | $7.16 | - |\n| Sales | $314.15 | $62.83 | +400% |\n| Orders | 5 | 1 | +400% |\n| CVR | 50.0% | 11.1% | +38.9pp |\n| ACOS | 2.4% | 11.4% | -9pp |\n| ROAS | 41.0x | 8.8x | +32.2x |\n\n**Why Increase Modifier:**\n- **Extraordinary 50% CVR at TOS** - best in dataset\n- 5x better ROAS at top placement\n- Only 5% of impressions at TOS despite superior performance\n- Category targeting works exceptionally well at top\n\n**Recommended Modifier**: +200% (3x base bid for TOS)\n- Increase TOS impression share from 5% to 20%\n- Expected additional spend: $30/month\n- Expected additional sales: $1,200/month\n- Projected ACOS: ~3%\n\n**Note**: This campaign is a goldmine - 50% CVR is exceptional. Maximize TOS exposure.\n\n---\n\n### 4. Hornady-Fireproof_Keypad_Safe-NB-Auto\n**Current TOS Share**: 5% of impressions (4,121 of 79,255)\n\n| Metric | Top of Search | Rest of Search | Difference |\n|--------|---------------|----------------|------------|\n| Spend | $82.93 | $858.46 | - |\n| Sales | $2,895.02 | $3,503.28 | - |\n| Orders | 16 | 20 | - |\n| CVR | 18.6% | 2.6% | +16pp |\n| ACOS | 2.9% | 24.5% | -21.6pp |\n| ROAS | 34.9x | 4.1x | +30.8x |\n\n**Why Increase Modifier:**\n- TOS delivers 8.5x better ROAS despite only 9% of spend\n- 7x higher CVR at top placement\n- Auto-targeting performing well but needs TOS focus\n- Rest of search at 24.5% ACOS is above target\n\n**Recommended Modifier**: +150% (2.5x base bid for TOS)\n- Increase TOS impression share from 5% to 15%\n- Expected additional spend: $250/month\n- Expected additional sales: $8,000/month\n- Projected ACOS: ~3.5%\n\n**Strategy**: Shift budget from product pages to TOS for better efficiency\n\n---\n\n### 5. GuardianSports-GX_Loop_Headgear-Branded-EXACT\n**Current TOS Share**: 19% of impressions (297 of 1,593)\n\n| Metric | Top of Search | Rest of Search | Difference |\n|--------|---------------|----------------|------------|\n| Spend | $54.67 | $12.78 | - |\n| Sales | $1,784.37 | $62.83 | +2,740% |\n| Orders | 27 | 1 | +2,600% |\n| CVR | 22.3% | 6.7% | +15.6pp |\n| ACOS | 3.1% | 20.3% | -17.2pp |\n| ROAS | 32.6x | 4.9x | +27.7x |\n\n**Why Increase Modifier:**\n- TOS generates 97% of sales with 81% of spend\n- 3.3x higher CVR at top placement\n- Brand exact match - should dominate TOS\n- Already 19% TOS share but can push higher\n\n**Recommended Modifier**: +100% (2x base bid for TOS)\n- Increase TOS impression share from 19% to 40%\n- Expected additional spend: $60/month\n- Expected additional sales: $2,000/month\n- Projected ACOS: ~3.5%\n\n**Note**: Brand protection - ensure top position for branded searches\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Plan\n\n### Step 1: Set Placement Modifiers (Day 1)\n\n| Campaign | Current Modifier | New Modifier | Change |\n|----------|------------------|--------------|--------|\n| Hornady-Fireproof_Keypad_Safe-Branded-PHRASE | 0% | +150% | +150pp |\n| Hornady-Auto_Charge_Pro-Branded-PHRASE | 0% | +200% | +200pp |\n| Guardian Sports-GX_Loop-NB-CAT-ASIN-CNQ | 0% | +200% | +200pp |\n| Hornady-Fireproof_Keypad_Safe-NB-Auto | 0% | +150% | +150pp |\n| GuardianSports-GX_Loop-Branded-EXACT | 0% | +100% | +100pp |\n\n### Step 2: Consider Negative Modifiers for Rest of Search\n\nFor campaigns with very poor non-TOS performance:\n- Hornady-Auto_Charge_Pro: -50% modifier for product pages\n- Hornady-Fireproof_Keypad_Safe-NB-Auto: -30% modifier for product pages\n\n### Step 3: Monitor Performance (Week 1-2)\n\n**Daily Checks**:\n- TOS impression share increase\n- Average position improvement\n- ACOS stability\n\n**Success Metrics**:\n- TOS impression share increases by 50-100%\n- Overall ACOS remains below 5%\n- Sales increase by 30-50%\n\n### Step 4: Optimize (Week 3-4)\n\n- If ACOS remains low (<3%), increase modifiers further\n- If impression share doesn't increase, check bid competitiveness\n- Consider reducing rest-of-search bids to fund TOS increases\n\n---\n\n## Expected Impact\n\n**Current Performance** (5 campaigns):\n- Total Spend: $1,173\n- Total Sales: $11,195\n- Total ACOS: 10.5%\n- TOS Share: 5-20%\n\n**After Modifier Adjustments**:\n- Total Spend: $1,673 (+43%)\n- Total Sales: $30,000 (+168%)\n- Total ACOS: 5.6% (-47%)\n- TOS Share: 15-40%\n\n**Net Benefit**:\n- Additional $500/month spend generates $18,800 additional sales\n- ROAS improves from 9.5x to 17.9x\n- All campaigns remain highly profitable (<6% ACOS)\n\n---\n\n## Key Takeaways\n\n1. **Top-of-search dramatically outperforms** other placements for these campaigns (10-50x better ROAS)\n2. **Brand campaigns** show strongest TOS performance - protect these positions\n3. **Auto-targeting** benefits significantly from TOS focus\n4. **Current TOS share is too low** (4-20%) given performance differential\n5. **Placement modifiers are free money** - no reason not to implement immediately\n"
