          "label": "Sonnet 4.6",
          "content": "# SP Auto-Targeting: Match Type Bid Reduction Recommendations\n\n**Data window:** 2026-04-09 – 2026-05-08 (30 days)  \n**Account:** Firefly Buys (`amzn1.ads-account.g.bj313q92siafngzbl54ewi56r`)  \n**Report rows (auto-targeting only):** 22 rows across 6 campaigns  \n**Total ad spend (auto-targeting):** $3,008.12 | **Total sales:** $14,634.56\n\n---\n\n## Methodology\n\nFor SP auto-targeting, Amazon maps four predefined match types: **close-match**, **loose-match**, **substitutes**, and **complements**. A bid reduction (or zeroing) is recommended when:\n\n- **ACoS is very high and there are sufficient clicks** (meaningful spend with poor return) → reduce bid\n- **Spend with zero sales and high click volume** → reduce or zero bid  \n- **Zero impressions / negligible spend** → monitor; not actionable yet\n\nBenchmark: account-level blended ACoS across all auto match types = ~20.6% (total cost $3,008 / total sales $14,635).\n\n---\n\n## Campaign-Level Analysis\n\n### 1. AngelGuard-Catch_All-NB-Auto (`429388688166206`)\n\n| Match Type | Impressions | Clicks | Spend | Sales | ACoS | ROAS | Recommendation |\n|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|\n| close-match | 37,258 | 320 | $240.21 | $2,592.10 | **9.3%** | 10.79 | ✅ Keep / raise bid |\n| substitutes | 39,066 | 219 | $143.29 | $1,072.29 | **13.4%** | 7.48 | ✅ Keep |\n| loose-match | 15,408 | 92 | $54.94 | $192.40 | **28.6%** | 3.50 | ⚠️ **Reduce bid** |\n| complements | — | — | — | — | — | — | No data |\n\n**Action:** Reduce the **loose-match** bid. ACoS at 28.6% is 3× worse than close-match and significantly above campaign average. Note: complements never fired — monitor for future data.\n\n---\n\n### 2. GPS-Chillz_Pet_Pad-MULTI-NB-SP-Auto (`325095516153239`)\n\n| Match Type | Impressions | Clicks | Spend | Sales | ACoS | ROAS | Recommendation |\n|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|\n| substitutes | 10,407 | 36 | $19.57 | $234.91 | **8.3%** | 12.00 | ✅ Keep / raise bid |\n| loose-match | 8,751 | 111 | $60.11 | $464.40 | **12.9%** | 7.73 | ✅ Keep |\n| complements | 7,828 | 61 | $44.10 | $249.94 | **17.6%** | 5.67 | ✅ Keep (acceptable) |\n| close-match | 11,624 | 183 | $142.01 | $649.84 | **21.9%** | 4.58 | ⚠️ **Reduce bid** |\n\n**Action:** Reduce the **close-match** bid. At 21.9% ACoS it is the most expensive match type for this campaign yet generates lower ROAS than loose-match or substitutes. It still converts, so reduce (do not zero).\n\n---\n\n### 3. Guardian Sports-GC-MULTI-NB-SP-AUTO (`527897003038750`)\n\n| Match Type | Impressions | Clicks | Spend | Sales | ACoS | ROAS | Recommendation |\n|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|\n| substitutes | 22,111 | 116 | $39.60 | $489.95 | **8.1%** | 12.37 | ✅ Keep / raise bid |\n| loose-match | 12,282 | 68 | $26.58 | $224.97 | **11.8%** | 8.46 | ✅ Keep |\n| close-match | 12,826 | 40 | $26.28 | $0.00 | **N/A** | 0.00 | 🚫 **Set bid to zero / pause** |\n| complements | — | — | — | — | — | — | No data |\n\n**Action:** **Set close-match bid to zero.** 40 clicks and $26.28 spend yielded zero sales — this match type is not converting for this campaign. Complements has no data yet; monitor.\n\n---\n\n### 4. Hornady-Fireproof_Keypad_Safe-B09TQ2CW9L-NB-SP-Auto (`249653366787409`)\n\n| Match Type | Impressions | Clicks | Spend | Sales | ACoS | ROAS | Recommendation |\n|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|\n| loose-match | 34,875 | 372 | $374.84 | $2,880.48 | **13.0%** | 7.68 | ✅ Keep |\n| close-match | 40,599 | 413 | $496.74 | $2,977.15 | **16.7%** | 5.99 | ✅ Keep (slightly elevated) |\n| substitutes | 643 | 1 | $0.91 | $0.00 | N/A | 0.00 | ⚠️ **Reduce bid** (low volume, $0 return) |\n| complements | 3 | 0 | $0.00 | $0.00 | N/A | 0.00 | Monitor (negligible) |\n\n**Action:** Reduce the **substitutes** bid. Only 1 click and $0 in sales; the match type is serving poorly-targeted impressions. Complements is negligible — monitor.\n\n---\n\n### 5. Hornady-Rapid_Safe_Night_Guard-B081DK7DQH-NB-SP-Auto (`315780136382832`)\n\n| Match Type | Impressions | Clicks | Spend | Sales | ACoS | ROAS | Recommendation |\n|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|\n| substitutes | 6,968 | 42 | $24.27 | $19.99 | **121.4%** | 0.82 | 🚫 **Set bid to zero / pause** |\n| close-match | 29,430 | 223 | $237.40 | $389.90 | **60.9%** | 1.64 | ⚠️ **Reduce bid significantly** |\n| loose-match | 158,548 | 876 | $744.02 | $1,949.50 | **38.2%** | 2.62 | ⚠️ **Reduce bid** |\n| complements | 39 | 0 | $0.00 | $0.00 | N/A | 0.00 | Monitor (negligible) |\n\n**Action:** This is the highest-risk campaign overall.\n- **Substitutes → set to zero:** 121% ACoS, nearly 7× unprofitable.\n- **Close-match → reduce bid significantly:** 60.9% ACoS on $237 spend; most costly per sale.\n- **Loose-match → reduce bid:** 38.2% ACoS on the highest spend in the account ($744); large savings opportunity.\n\n---\n\n### 6. SnapSafe-Treklite_Gun_Safe_Lock_Box-MULTI-NB-SP-Auto (`163227330068953`)\n\n| Match Type | Impressions | Clicks | Spend | Sales | ACoS | ROAS | Recommendation |\n|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|\n| complements | 1,204 | 4 | $2.42 | $0.00 | N/A | 0.00 | ⚠️ **Reduce bid** |\n| close-match | 10,396 | 78 | $70.38 | $70.77 | **99.4%** | 1.01 | 🚫 **Set bid to zero / pause** |\n| loose-match | 43,614 | 295 | $260.45 | $175.97 | **148.0%** | 0.68 | 🚫 **Set bid to zero / pause** |\n| substitutes | 10 | 0 | $0.00 | $0.00 | N/A | 0.00 | Monitor (negligible) |\n\n**Action:** This campaign is deeply unprofitable across all active match types.\n- **Loose-match → zero/pause:** 148% ACoS, $260 spend, only $176 returned — worst single match-type in the account.\n- **Close-match → zero/pause:** 99.4% ACoS on $70 spend.\n- **Complements → reduce bid:** only 4 clicks with no sales; small but wasteful.\n\n---\n\n## Summary Table — Bid Actions\n\n| Campaign | Match Type | Spend | ACoS | Recommendation |\n|---|---|---|---|---|\n| AngelGuard-Catch_All-NB-Auto | loose-match | $54.94 | 28.6% | Reduce bid |\n| GPS-Chillz_Pet_Pad-MULTI-NB-SP-Auto | close-match | $142.01 | 21.9% | Reduce bid |\n| Guardian Sports-GC-MULTI-NB-SP-AUTO | close-match | $26.28 | ∞ (0 sales) | **Set to zero** |\n| Hornady-Fireproof_Keypad_Safe | substitutes | $0.91 | ∞ (0 sales) | Reduce bid |\n| Hornady-Rapid_Safe_Night_Guard | substitutes | $24.27 | 121.4% | **Set to zero** |\n| Hornady-Rapid_Safe_Night_Guard | close-match | $237.40 | 60.9% | Reduce bid significantly |\n| Hornady-Rapid_Safe_Night_Guard | loose-match | $744.02 | 38.2% | Reduce bid |\n| SnapSafe-Treklite_Lock_Box | loose-match | $260.45 | 148.0% | **Set to zero** |\n| SnapSafe-Treklite_Lock_Box | close-match | $70.38 | 99.4% | **Set to zero** |\n| SnapSafe-Treklite_Lock_Box | complements | $2.42 | ∞ (0 sales) | Reduce bid |\n\n---\n\n## Reasoning\n\n**\"Set to zero\" threshold:** Applied when ACoS exceeds ~100% (spend > revenue) or spend with zero sales and sufficient clicks (≥10) to be statistically meaningful.\n\n**\"Reduce bid\" threshold:** Applied when ACoS materially exceeds the account blended rate (~20%) or the campaign's best-performing match type by >1.5×.\n\n**Preserved match types:** Any match type with ACoS ≤ ~20% or ROAS ≥ 5 was left untouched or flagged for a potential bid increase.\n\nThe largest waste driver is `Hornady-Rapid_Safe_Night_Guard` loose-match ($744 spend, ROAS 2.62) — even a modest bid reduction here would recover meaningful budget.\n"
