          "content": "# SB Video Campaign Expansion: ASIN Recommendations Based on SP Performance\n\n**Question ID:** EV201  \n**Data window:** 2026-04-09 – 2026-05-08 (30 days)  \n**Account:** Firefly Buys (`amzn1.ads-account.g.bj313q92siafngzbl54ewi56r`)\n\n---\n\n## Existing SB Video Campaign\n\n| Campaign | SBV ASIN | SBV Purchases (30d) | SBV Sales |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| DelkProducts-FrostGuard_Plus_Snowflake_Standard-B09J7C24MB-NB-SBV-EXACT | B09J68485T | 1 | $20.99 |\n\nThe single SB Video campaign is for the **Delk Products / FrostGuard** brand. The currently promoted ASIN (**B09J68485T**, the Snowflake Standard variant) recorded **zero SP-attributed purchases** in the trailing 30 days, which is a key gap this expansion should address.\n\n---\n\n## SP Performance Data\n\n- **Total SP report rows:** 867  \n- **Total SP purchases (all brands):** 5,362  \n- **Total SP sales (all brands):** $257,205  \n- **Delk/FrostGuard SP rows analyzed:** 17  \n- **Unique Delk ASINs with SP conversions:** 13  \n\n---\n\n## Recommended ASINs for SBV Expansion\n\nAll candidates ranked by SP purchases in the last 30 days; none are currently in the SBV campaign.\n\n| Rank | ASIN | SP Purchases | SP Sales | Units | Avg. Order Value | Parent ASIN | Primary SP Campaign |\n|---:|---|---:|---:|---:|---:|---|---|\n| 1 | **B07YP85FZM** | **11** | **$384.89** | **11** | **$34.99** | B08R6DR6LV | FrostGuard_Plus_Black_XL (NB-Exact) + Branded Phrase |\n| 2 | **B07YP7QZZW** | **4** | **$139.96** | **4** | **$34.99** | B08R6DR6LV | FrostGuard Branded Phrase |\n| 3 | **B07YR5LF37** | **3** | **$159.96** | **4** | **$53.32** | B08R6CWDJ8 | FrostGuard_Plus_Black_XL + Branded Phrase |\n| 4 | **B09GRY3NGH** | **3** | **$159.96** | **4** | **$53.32** | B08R6CWDJ8 | FrostGuard_Plus_Black_XL + Branded Phrase |\n| 5 | B08YWTPG1H | 2 | $43.98 | 2 | $21.99 | — | FrostGuard_All (NB-Exact) |\n| 6 | B09THLGM5Y | 1 | $299.99 | 1 | $299.99 | — | UrbanTransit Rolling Stool (different product line) |\n\n> **Priority focus: B07YP85FZM, B07YP7QZZW, B07YR5LF37, B09GRY3NGH**\n\n---\n\n## Conversion Justification\n\n### #1 Priority — B07YP85FZM (FrostGuard Plus Black XL)\n- Highest SP purchase volume across the brand: **11 purchases / $384.89 in 30 days**.\n- Converting across two distinct SP campaigns (dedicated NB-Exact campaign *and* Branded Phrase), proving demand from both new and repeat shoppers.\n- Same parent (B08R6DR6LV) as B07YP7QZZW — pairing them in a SBV ad could lift both variants.\n- The current SBV ASIN (B09J68485T) had **0 SP purchases**; B07YP85FZM had 11× more, making it the strongest replacement/addition candidate.\n\n### #2 Priority — B07YP7QZZW (FrostGuard Plus, same parent as #1)\n- **4 SP purchases / $139.96**, all from Branded Phrase traffic — validated by shoppers actively searching the brand.\n- Shares parent ASIN B08R6DR6LV with B07YP85FZM; featuring siblings in SBV increases coverage of the parent detail page.\n\n### #3 & #4 Priority — B07YR5LF37 and B09GRY3NGH (FrostGuard Plus Black XL variants, parent B08R6CWDJ8)\n- Tied at **3 SP purchases / $159.96 each**, converting across both Branded and NB-Exact campaigns.\n- Higher AOV ($53.32 vs $34.99) than the top-two, suggesting upsell potential in video creative.\n- Both share parent B08R6CWDJ8 — co-featuring them anchors video content to the Plus Black XL line.\n\n### NTB Data\nThe SP report did not return New-to-Brand purchase values for any Delk ASIN rows (fields returned `null`). This is consistent with SP NTB data not always being available at the product-conversion level without a dedicated brand analytics report. Conversion volume and AOV alone are used for ranking.\n\n---\n\n## Reasoning Summary\n\nThe SBV campaign is currently live with ASIN B09J68485T (Snowflake Standard) but that ASIN had **no measurable SP conversion activity** in the last 30 days. The top SP converters in the FrostGuard line are the **Black XL variants** (B07YP85FZM, B07YP7QZZW, B07YR5LF37, B09GRY3NGH), which collectively drove **21 SP purchases and $844.77 in sales** in the same period. Adding these ASINs to the SBV campaign expands upper-funnel video coverage to products that already demonstrate lower-funnel conversion strength in SP — the classic indicator for profitable SB Video investment.\n"
